text: The Egypt women's national handball team is the national team of Egypt. It is governed by the Egyptian Handball Federation and takes part in international handball competitions. ==African Championship record== *1974 – 3rd *1981 – 6th *1983 – 8th *1985 – 7th *1987 – 6th *1989 – 5th *1991 – 7th *2004 – 6th *2010 – 6th *2012 – 9th ==External links== * *IHF profile Category:Women's national handball teams Handball National team
